Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.25,0:00:08.96,utaware def,,0,0,0,,Must you go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:09.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしても帰るのか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:13.04,utaware def,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I would like to stay,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:13.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できることなら 一緒にいたかったんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:16.88,utaware def,,0,0,0,,but we were born and raised in Yamayura,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.15,0:00:17.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは 生まれも育ちも\Nヤマユラだからなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.88,0:00:19.58,utaware def,,0,0,0,,so we would like to die there too.
